title: Bakers Guild Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Organic, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bakery and cafe in downtown. Offers a small breakfast menu plus soups, salads, sandwiches, and pizza all featuring its self-produced sprouted grain bread. Vegans could get the sprouted chickpea hummus, black bean burger, sprouted wheat salad, Thai salad with peanut dressing, and usually the soup du jour. Specify.
